api_data.heading: Covid County Site Selection
api_data.title_text:
The pricing system in Finland for reimbursed products is tender based and changes quarterly.

The local team is interested in:

  • Identifying patterns in price changes for products in Finland
  • Develop a way to optimize Pfizer price submissions to provide competitive edge against local companies in Finland such as Orion (strong local preference to this company)?

This analysis focuses on identifying patterns in price change and recommending reference prices using historical data.


Data used is from Jan’17 to May’19.
For Non-Upjohn Products, data used is for non branded products only

Hover over bubbles to see sales value of different companies for the above time period
